long_description: at bridge park montessori, we aim to ensure that our children have everything they need at their fingertips in order to reach their full potential. with the help of 100% qualified staff, we guide each child at their own pace. we have a full range of montessori materials that are readily available for the children to use on a daily basis. we also have a great outdoor space for the children to play as well for growing our own fruit and vegetables. some of the produce that we are currently growing include strawberries, carrots, tomatoes, spinach, chives, pepper and sunflowers. we have chickens and cockerels also for children to collect the eggs.
